25|$|Following {{the failure}} of the first short lived Transatlantic {{telegraph}} cable of 1858, a second, more durable cable was completed in 1865, connecting Nova Scotia to England. By 1890 there was an international <b>telegraph</b> <b>network.</b>|$|E
